comment: Missing pipeline-job, the developer is unfamiliar with the project as this is change his first change in the project ('Requirements'). R1: I don't see requirements check jobs configured for these projects in openstack-infra/project-config. Please set those up first and make sure you're in sync with the global requirements, before adding this patch. R2: There's no check-requirements job for these projects. Please add the jobs to project-config first. D: I sent a patch adding check-requirements jobs as you requested: [216161] Please let me know if anything else is missing.
